Program: Omnibus
Title: Deep Heat
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376jt9
Last Broadcast Date: 13 March 1990
Discussing hydrothermal vents and the animals and landscapes found there. Guests include Alvin Expedition leader, Dudley Foster, Geoffrey Thompson of Oceanographic Institution, Woods Hole and James Childress of the University of California.